segment.source: This event generates when event logging service encountered an error while processing an incoming event.
segment.target: This event generates when event logging service encountered an error while processing an incoming event.

segment.source: It typically generates when logging service will not be able to correctly write the event to the event log or some parameters were not passed to logging service to log the event correctly.
segment.target: It typically generates when logging service will not be able to correctly write the event to the event log or some parameters were not passed to logging service to log the event correctly.

segment.source: You will typically see a defective or incorrect event before 1108.
segment.target: You will typically see a defective or incorrect event before 1108.
